OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Fthis evening and overnight with clear
OL,7,Fspells. A few patchy mist and fog
OL,8,Freforming. Strengthening breezes
OL,9,Faround coasts and hills. A cool night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FSome sunshine possible in
OL,12,Fthe east, where feeling very mild.
OL,13,FTemperatures suppressed slightly in
OL,14,Fthe west as cloud thickens ahead of
OL,15,Frain arriving later, heavy at times
OL,16,Finitially.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
