OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:
OL,6,FOccasional patchy rain and drizzle in
OL,7,Fplaces, but mostly dry albeit often
OL,8,Fcloudy. Cloud breaking at times to
OL,9,Fgive some warm sunshine though less
OL,10,Fmild and chilly by night.
